event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event TimelockExecutionStrategySetUp(address owner, address vetoGuardian, address[] spaces, uint256 quorum, uint256 timelockDelay)
event TransactionExecuted(tuple(address to, uint256 value, bytes data, uint8 operation, uint256 salt) transaction)
event TransactionQueued(tuple(address to, uint256 value, bytes data, uint8 operation, uint256 salt) transaction, uint256 executionTime)

function execute(tuple(uint32 snapshotTimestamp, uint32 startTimestamp, uint32 minEndTimestamp, uint32 maxEndTimestamp, bytes32 executionPayloadHash, address executionStrategy, address author, uint8 finalizationStatus, uint256 activeVotingStrategies) proposal, uint256 votesFor, uint256 votesAgainst, uint256 votesAbstain, bytes payload)

function getProposalStatus(tuple(uint32 snapshotTimestamp, uint32 startTimestamp, uint32 minEndTimestamp, uint32 maxEndTimestamp, bytes32 executionPayloadHash, address executionStrategy, address author, uint8 finalizationStatus, uint256 activeVotingStrategies) proposal, uint256 votesFor, uint256 votesAgainst, uint256 votesAbstain) view returns (uint8)
function onERC1155BatchReceived(address, address, uint256[], uint256[], bytes) pure returns (bytes4)
function onERC1155Received(address, address, uint256, uint256, bytes) pure returns (bytes4)
function onERC721Received(address, address, uint256, bytes) pure returns (bytes4)
